OL,7,FHealth Trusts are to pay consultants
OL,8,Fup to #220 per hour to cover for
OL,9,Fstriking junior doctors, UTV can
OL,10,Freveal.
OL,12,FJunior doctors across Northern Ireland
OL,13,Fare due to stage a 24-hour strike from
OL,14,F8am on Wednesday in a dispute over pay.
OL,16,FSome consultants who agree to cover
OL,17,Fshifts during the walkout could earn
OL,18,Fas much as #1,760 for an eight hour
OL,19,Fshift.
