OL,7,FA letter from Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fservices to all Health Trusts - seen
OL,9,Fby UTV - said: "As an exceptional
OL,10,Fmeasure we have agreed to escalate
OL,11,Frates of pay for work performed during
OL,12,Fthe industrial action which is
OL,13,Fexpected to be outside of job plan and/
OL,14,For the grade they would normally be
OL,15,Fexpected to work."
OL,17,FThe letter outlines the temporary pay
OL,18,Frates, which include #110 per hour for
OL,19,Fa daytime consultant, up to #220 per
OL,20,Fhour for an out of hours consultant.
